./sdp/verification/t-009@20260425t183959z-verify.md:78:{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":"2026-04-25T22:04:04.458Z","tool_name":"write_file","tool_id":"write_file_1777154644458_0","parameters":{"content":"# Verification Report — T-009 @sdp/logs/Verify_T-009_20260425T183959Z_1777154579.log\n\n**Verify Agent:** Gemini CLI\n**Date:** 2026-04-25\n**Artifacts Reviewed:**\n- `my-claw/tools/sample_capture_daemon.py`\n- `tests/test_sample_capture_daemon.py`\n- `my-claw/tools/first_boot.py`\n- `ESCALATIONS.md`\n\n## Correctness\nThe implementation correctly handles mono WAV export at 24-bit 48 kHz. Peak normalization to -1 dBFS is applied as required, with a -30 dBFS floor for raw preservation. Filenames follow the pattern `<source>_<YYYYMMDDTHHMMSSZ>_<arc>_<sampleid>.wav`. Database records in `index.sqlite` include the `gain_db` adjustment.\n\n## Completeness\nAll acceptance criteria are met. The `save_capture` function integrates tag extraction, normalization, and persistence. Tests comprehensively cover file format, normalization logic, and database insertion.\n\n## Consistency\nThe code adheres to established project patterns for JACK interaction and SQLite indexing. The use of `numpy` for audio processing and `wave` for export is consistent with existing toolsets.\n\n## Security\nNo security vulnerabilities or leaked credentials were identified. Use of `uuid.uuid4().hex` for sample IDs provides collision-resistant identifiers.\n\n## Quality\nThe code is modular and well-documented. Hardening requirements for `bootstrap_identity` were successfully integrated into the daemon startup flow and verified.\n\n## Issues Found\n- [x] (Resolved) Manual verification initially failed due to using a non-standard arc phase (\"test\"), but the coercion to \"unknown\" was confirmed as correct behavior per specification.\n\n## Verdict: PASS\n\n## Notes for Lead Agent\nThe implementation is solid. The peak normalization floor (-30 dBFS) correctly prevents boosting low-level noise floors. The identity bootstrapping hardening is correctly placed at the entry point of the daemon's main loop.\n","file_path":"sdp/verification/t-009 @20260425t183959z-verify.md"}}
